an><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right:36.0pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">ü<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span lang=\"FA\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;\">گروه\r\nشهید قورچی زاده، شهرستان سیریک، بخش بمانی</span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right:36.0pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">ü<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span lang=\"FA\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;\">گروه\r\nماوا، شهرستان خوی، بخش فیرورق<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:15.7pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:kashida;text-kashida:0%;line-height:normal\"><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font